@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zytnyl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp((0.91 / wp.abs(v1 + 0.21)))
    tmp = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.52 + v1 + 0.78) / tmp))
    v2 = wp.exp((v0 / (v1 + 0.38 + tmp + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
